  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799950/extras/94b0676a232e1c6a79921dd8cbe1667a.webp?t=1762826287\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The students aren't learning, and they are failing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a teacher, you came up with an idea to make them study─</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And it's rock, paper, scissors!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Win the game to force them to detention.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play rock, paper, scissors with your students!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799950/extras/456d9f0ad4d96183ed2338df36bc8b1b.webp?t=1762826287\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a game of rock, paper, scissors! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Win three times to beat the game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Click on the three options, rock, paper, and scissors with the mouse,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >and as long as you win three times, you give them a detention,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >but if you lose three times, you can only watch them leave.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Win the game to make them study during detention!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799950/extras/94b0676a232e1c6a79921dd8cbe1667a.webp?t=1762826287\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The students aren't learning, and they are failing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a teacher, you came up with an idea to make them study─</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And it's rock, paper, scissors!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Win the game to force them to detention.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play rock, paper, scissors with your students!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2799950/extras/456d9f0ad4d96183ed2338df36bc8b1b.webp?t=1762826287\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a game of rock, paper, scissors! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Win three times to beat the game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Click on the three options, rock, paper, and scissors with the mouse,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >and as long as you win three times, you give them a detention,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >but if you lose three times, you can only watch them leave.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Win the game to make them study during detention!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
